[
    {
        "index": 1,
        "start_time": 6875,
        "end_time": 11097,
        "text": "Your cell phone is mainly made\nof plastics and metals."
    },
    {
        "index": 2,
        "start_time": 11097,
        "end_time": 13674,
        "text": "It&#39;s easy to appreciate \nthe inventive process"
    },
    {
        "index": 3,
        "start_time": 13674,
        "end_time": 18941,
        "text": "by which those elements are made to add up\nto something so useful and entertaining."
    },
    {
        "index": 4,
        "start_time": 18941,
        "end_time": 21746,
        "text": "But there&#39;s another story \nwe don&#39;t hear about as much."
    },
    {
        "index": 5,
        "start_time": 21746,
        "end_time": 24933,
        "text": "How did we get our raw ingredients\nin the first place"
    },
    {
        "index": 6,
        "start_time": 24933,
        "end_time": 28802,
        "text": "from the chaotic tangle of materials\nthat is nature?"
    },
    {
        "index": 7,
        "start_time": 28802,
        "end_time": 33431,
        "text": "The answer is a group of clever hacks\nknown as separation techniques."
    },
    {
        "index": 8,
        "start_time": 33431,
        "end_time": 37489,
        "text": "They work by taking advantage\nof the fundamental properties of things"
    },
    {
        "index": 9,
        "start_time": 37489,
        "end_time": 40124,
        "text": "to disentangle them from each other."
    },
    {
        "index": 10,
        "start_time": 40124,
        "end_time": 43959,
        "text": "Simple separation techniques\napply to many physical scenarios,"
    },
    {
        "index": 11,
        "start_time": 43959,
        "end_time": 45791,
        "text": "like separating cream from milk,"
    },
    {
        "index": 12,
        "start_time": 45791,
        "end_time": 47920,
        "text": "extracting water from soil,"
    },
    {
        "index": 13,
        "start_time": 47920,
        "end_time": 52138,
        "text": "or even sifting out flecks of gold\nfrom river sand."
    },
    {
        "index": 14,
        "start_time": 52138,
        "end_time": 55420,
        "text": "But not all mixtures \nare so easy to unravel."
    },
    {
        "index": 15,
        "start_time": 55420,
        "end_time": 56836,
        "text": "In some of those cases,"
    },
    {
        "index": 16,
        "start_time": 56836,
        "end_time": 61499,
        "text": "we can exploit the differences between\nphysical properties within a mixture,"
    },
    {
        "index": 17,
        "start_time": 61499,
        "end_time": 63176,
        "text": "like particle size,"
    },
    {
        "index": 18,
        "start_time": 63176,
        "end_time": 64112,
        "text": "density,"
    },
    {
        "index": 19,
        "start_time": 64112,
        "end_time": 65684,
        "text": "or boiling point"
    },
    {
        "index": 20,
        "start_time": 65684,
        "end_time": 67712,
        "text": "to extract what&#39;s required."
    },
    {
        "index": 21,
        "start_time": 67712,
        "end_time": 68876,
        "text": "Take petroleum,"
    },
    {
        "index": 22,
        "start_time": 68876,
        "end_time": 71581,
        "text": "a mixture of different \ntypes of hydrocarbons."
    },
    {
        "index": 23,
        "start_time": 71581,
        "end_time": 73448,
        "text": "Some of these are valuable as fuels,"
    },
    {
        "index": 24,
        "start_time": 73448,
        "end_time": 77665,
        "text": "and others make good raw materials\nfor generating electric power."
    },
    {
        "index": 25,
        "start_time": 77665,
        "end_time": 81491,
        "text": "To separate them, experts rely on one\nimportant feature:"
    },
    {
        "index": 26,
        "start_time": 81491,
        "end_time": 85676,
        "text": "different hydrocarbons boil \nat different temperatures."
    },
    {
        "index": 27,
        "start_time": 85676,
        "end_time": 89925,
        "text": "During the boiling process,\neach type vaporizes at a precise point,"
    },
    {
        "index": 28,
        "start_time": 89925,
        "end_time": 92794,
        "text": "then gets separately funneled \ninto a container"
    },
    {
        "index": 29,
        "start_time": 92794,
        "end_time": 95947,
        "text": "and collected as a liquid as it cools."
    },
    {
        "index": 30,
        "start_time": 95947,
        "end_time": 98776,
        "text": "Separation techniques \nalso take us to the sea."
    },
    {
        "index": 31,
        "start_time": 98776,
        "end_time": 100804,
        "text": "In some drought-stricken countries,"
    },
    {
        "index": 32,
        "start_time": 100804,
        "end_time": 104024,
        "text": "the ocean is the only \navailable water source."
    },
    {
        "index": 33,
        "start_time": 104024,
        "end_time": 106883,
        "text": "But of course,\nhumans can&#39;t drink salt water."
    },
    {
        "index": 34,
        "start_time": 106883,
        "end_time": 108658,
        "text": "One way to get around this problem"
    },
    {
        "index": 35,
        "start_time": 108658,
        "end_time": 112877,
        "text": "is to remove salt from sea water \nwith reverse osmosis,"
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "start_time": 112877,
        "end_time": 116869,
        "text": "a process that separates \nwater&#39;s ingredients by size."
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "start_time": 116869,
        "end_time": 120405,
        "text": "A membrane with pores \nbigger than water particles,"
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "start_time": 120405,
        "end_time": 122560,
        "text": "but smaller than salt particles,"
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "start_time": 122560,
        "end_time": 125430,
        "text": "only lets fresh water pass through,"
    },
    {
        "index": 40,
        "start_time": 125430,
        "end_time": 129263,
        "text": "transforming what was once undrinkable\ninto a life saver."
    },
    {
        "index": 41,
        "start_time": 129263,
        "end_time": 131093,
        "text": "Meanwhile in the medical world,"
    },
    {
        "index": 42,
        "start_time": 131093,
        "end_time": 135282,
        "text": "blood tests are a vital tool \nfor evaluating a person&#39;s health,"
    },
    {
        "index": 43,
        "start_time": 135282,
        "end_time": 137921,
        "text": "but doctors typically \ncan&#39;t examine blood samples"
    },
    {
        "index": 44,
        "start_time": 137921,
        "end_time": 140527,
        "text": "until they&#39;ve separated \nthe solid blood cells"
    },
    {
        "index": 45,
        "start_time": 140527,
        "end_time": 143169,
        "text": "from the liquid plasma \nthey&#39;re dissolved in."
    },
    {
        "index": 46,
        "start_time": 143169,
        "end_time": 147902,
        "text": "To do that, a powerful rotational force\nis exerted on the test tube,"
    },
    {
        "index": 47,
        "start_time": 147902,
        "end_time": 150861,
        "text": "causing heavier substances \nwith higher density,"
    },
    {
        "index": 48,
        "start_time": 150861,
        "end_time": 152244,
        "text": "like blood cells,"
    },
    {
        "index": 49,
        "start_time": 152244,
        "end_time": 155236,
        "text": "to move away from the rotational axis."
    },
    {
        "index": 50,
        "start_time": 155236,
        "end_time": 158267,
        "text": "Meanwhile, lighter substances \nwith lower density,"
    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "start_time": 158267,
        "end_time": 159486,
        "text": "like plasma,"
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "start_time": 159486,
        "end_time": 161545,
        "text": "move to its center."
    },
    {
        "index": 53,
        "start_time": 161545,
        "end_time": 163611,
        "text": "The tube&#39;s contents divide clearly,"
    },
    {
        "index": 54,
        "start_time": 163611,
        "end_time": 168016,
        "text": "and the blood cells and liquid plasma\ncan be tested independently."
    },
    {
        "index": 55,
        "start_time": 168016,
        "end_time": 171306,
        "text": "But sometimes, unlike oil,\nseawater, and blood,"
    },
    {
        "index": 56,
        "start_time": 171306,
        "end_time": 173712,
        "text": "the parts of mixtures \nthat we want to separate"
    },
    {
        "index": 57,
        "start_time": 173712,
        "end_time": 176287,
        "text": "share the same physical properties."
    },
    {
        "index": 58,
        "start_time": 176287,
        "end_time": 181406,
        "text": "In these cases, the only way to isolate \ningredients is by chemical separation,"
    },
    {
        "index": 59,
        "start_time": 181406,
        "end_time": 185074,
        "text": "a complex process that relies \non unique interactions"
    },
    {
        "index": 60,
        "start_time": 185074,
        "end_time": 189322,
        "text": "between components within a mixture\nand another material."
    },
    {
        "index": 61,
        "start_time": 189322,
        "end_time": 191995,
        "text": "One of these methods is chromatography,"
    },
    {
        "index": 62,
        "start_time": 191995,
        "end_time": 196023,
        "text": "a tool forensic scientists use \nto examine crime scenes."
    },
    {
        "index": 63,
        "start_time": 196023,
        "end_time": 198566,
        "text": "They dissolve gathered evidence in a gas,"
    },
    {
        "index": 64,
        "start_time": 198566,
        "end_time": 201334,
        "text": "and can monitor \nand analyze the ingredients"
    },
    {
        "index": 65,
        "start_time": 201334,
        "end_time": 204774,
        "text": "as they separate \nand move at varying speeds"
    },
    {
        "index": 66,
        "start_time": 204774,
        "end_time": 206930,
        "text": "due to their unique chemical properties."
    },
    {
        "index": 67,
        "start_time": 206930,
        "end_time": 211630,
        "text": "That information then tells scientists\nprecisely what was present at the scene,"
    },
    {
        "index": 68,
        "start_time": 211630,
        "end_time": 214333,
        "text": "often helping to identify the culprit."
    },
    {
        "index": 69,
        "start_time": 214333,
        "end_time": 217298,
        "text": "Separation techniques are not just about\nindustry,"
    },
    {
        "index": 70,
        "start_time": 217298,
        "end_time": 218257,
        "text": "infrastructure,"
    },
    {
        "index": 71,
        "start_time": 218257,
        "end_time": 219195,
        "text": "medicine,"
    },
    {
        "index": 72,
        "start_time": 219195,
        "end_time": 220518,
        "text": "and justice."
    },
    {
        "index": 73,
        "start_time": 220518,
        "end_time": 223867,
        "text": "One of the most technically ambitious\nprojects in human history"
    },
    {
        "index": 74,
        "start_time": 223867,
        "end_time": 228528,
        "text": "is a separation technique aimed at\nanswering the fundamental question,"
    },
    {
        "index": 75,
        "start_time": 228528,
        "end_time": 231237,
        "text": "&quot;What is the Universe made of?&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 76,
        "start_time": 231237,
        "end_time": 234158,
        "text": "By accelerating particles \nto extremely high speeds"
    },
    {
        "index": 77,
        "start_time": 234158,
        "end_time": 236188,
        "text": "and smashing them into each other,"
    },
    {
        "index": 78,
        "start_time": 236188,
        "end_time": 240443,
        "text": "we can break them into \ntheir constituent parts ever so briefly."
    },
    {
        "index": 79,
        "start_time": 240443,
        "end_time": 242911,
        "text": "And if we succeed at that, what&#39;s next?"
    },
    {
        "index": 80,
        "start_time": 242911,
        "end_time": 245427,
        "text": "Is there a most elementary particle?"
    },
    {
        "index": 81,
        "start_time": 245427,
        "end_time": 248040,
        "text": "And if so, what&#39;s it made of?"
    }
]